This quiet path seems perfect for taking a quiet stroll. There are more sun-warmed flat rocks here to lay upon.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT E 1185
EXIT ABOVE 1187
IFENTRY -1
   ECHO PLAYER This quiet place seems the perfect spot to reflect on things you have learned.
ENDIF

ITEM 0 411 ADJ1=344 ADJ2=491
ITEM 1 74 VAL2=1183
IFPREVERB GO 1
    CLEARVERB
    MOVE 1183
ENDIF
IFPREVERB E -1
   IFVAR FLAG1 < 1
      CLEARVERB
      ECHO PLAYER You feel somewhat tired, perhaps you should take a break and Lay down on the nice warm rock.
   ELSE
      EQUAL FLAG1 0
   ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB LAY -1
     CLEARVERB
     POSITION LAY
     EQUAL ROUNDTIME 15
     ECHO PLAYER You step over to the flat rocks and lay down upon them. Within moments a soothing warmth spreads along your body.
     PLREVENT 1
     CONTPLREVENT
     ECHO PLAYER As you soak up the warmth from the rocks, you let your mind wander. You stare up at the sky and reflect upon your race's ability to FLY.
     PLREVENT 2
     CONTPLREVENT
     ECHO PLAYER You think about all the wonderful times when you would ASCEND and DESCEND the thermals as you flew from place to place.   
     CONTPLREVENT
     ECHO PLAYER You stand up refreshed, ready to begin again.
     ECHO PLAYER You may practice FLYing or continue EASTward.
     EQUAL FLAG1 1
     POSITION STAND
ENDIF
IFPREVERB GO 0 
