NUMBER 1187
NAME Aerial View, Drakin Island
AERIAL
FIXED_LIGHT
*DESCRIPTION_START
You are flying above the island, an exhilirating experience for you. Far down below you can make out several of the buildings of this small community. The horizon seems to continue on forever, you realize that this tiny island is but a speck lost in the great world of Andor. There is far more to this world than this small waystation of learning.
*DESCRIPTION_END

EXIT BELOW 1184
IFENTRY -1
   IFVAR INTNUM6 < 10   
      ECHO PLAYER You are now flying, some places such as this will have further exits from here, just like land exits. You can sometimes fly in any of the normal directions when you are in the air, to move in those directions, just type: NORTH, SOUTH, etc. whichever directions are available. To head back down, just type DESCEND, and DESCEND again, to land on the ground.
   ENDIF
ENDIF
